vim is a editor 

Permission 
Linux was designed to allow many users to access single system at the same time.
also files need to be protected.


Permissions are of 3 types
Read
Write
Execute


drwxr-xr-x 10 lco staff         320 28 Jul 23:04 lcodev
x - 1
w - 2
r - 4

chmod 755 filename